      According to this flow, users need to add the city one by one. Our system requires specific dates to generate planning itinerary. Therefore, after all the cities had been picked, users should select dates for each city manually. After presenting my design explorations with other designers, I found out that changing the way of date picking could help increase planning engagement. So I made a few changes in it. Since planning engagement ties closely with our revenue, I decided to make several wireframes to make the whole flow more intuitive.

